WEBVTT

00:07.810 --> 00:10.072
- Previously on "Get Shorty"...
- Did you show them the books?

00:10.148 --> 00:12.050
- Yeah.
- There it is!

00:12.102 --> 00:13.684
Money laundering, you...

00:13.979 --> 00:15.320
What if we tell L.A.

00:15.420 --> 00:17.282
that we can clean $30 million
of their money?

00:17.382 --> 00:20.525
You risk nothing,
and you make money off them.

00:20.625 --> 00:21.886
I'm making another movie.

00:21.986 --> 00:24.328
It needs to be privately financed.

00:24.428 --> 00:26.130
How close are you with L.A.?

00:26.230 --> 00:27.811
You want me to make an introduction?

00:27.911 --> 00:30.494
We require an additional 5%.

00:30.594 --> 00:33.296
- This a joke?
- It is not.

00:33.396 --> 00:35.779
So, these investors, they're...
they're friends of Amara's?

00:35.879 --> 00:37.100
Associates.

00:37.200 --> 00:38.581
Like her but just...

00:38.681 --> 00:40.103
on a bigger level?

00:40.203 --> 00:42.345
I wanted to update you on "Wylderness".

00:42.445 --> 00:44.627
Yeah, I'm past that.

00:44.727 --> 00:47.549
- Shit. What were you burning?
- Old photos.

00:47.650 --> 00:48.831
It's pretty.

00:48.931 --> 00:50.953
It's a witch's mirror.

00:51.053 --> 00:52.594
Oh. Does that make you a witch?

00:52.709 --> 00:54.804
Looks like Deborah Schaffer's kids.

00:54.828 --> 00:56.185
Deborah Schaffer the actress?

00:56.209 --> 00:57.238
Yeah.

00:57.338 --> 00:58.600
This is the divorce papers?

00:58.700 --> 01:00.802
There's a part about custody
on page two.

01:00.902 --> 01:02.964
You gonna take her away from me.

01:03.064 --> 01:04.765
When we first saw Rick,
he was frightened.

01:04.864 --> 01:06.967
I told him
we would use all our resources

01:07.067 --> 01:08.529
to make sure he wouldn't get hurt.

01:08.629 --> 01:11.772
I'm going to make a deal,
so if I were you,

01:11.872 --> 01:14.114
I'd make sure he's still
breathing when the feds come.

